question.title: How can I resolve "java: cannot find symbol" error on an Entity Query Service on a JHipster Generated App?
question.body:
I generated a JHipster app using Java for backend and whenever I try to run the app I get this error:

    root\service\TaskQueryService.java:78:93
java: cannot find symbol
  symbol:   variable Task_
  location: class ro.package.service.TaskQueryService

This is my TaskQueryService:

I found some people having the same issue but I still can't resolve it. Can someone explain to me what I'm doing wrong?
